        {
          "type": "work-header",
          "title": null,
          "subtitle": "I am an experienced graphic designer and developer. The combination of high fluency in both fields enables me to conceive, prototype and develop digital products, tools and services.\n\nMost recently I was Creative Director and Co-Founder of digital agency Make+Ship. Prior to that I was in-house designer and developer at The Guardian, UBS and The Times.\n\nIt is in my nature to make and craft things with attention to quality and detail. I always enjoy the journey starting from nothing to creating something useful, enjoyable or inspiring to others. \n\nAvailable for new projects from January 2022. \n",
