          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "work-row",
          "columns": [
            {
              "text": "I collaborated closely with users to prototype and develop an easily readable diagnostics interface including an innovative real-time minimum-spanning-tree visualisation of TB-relatedness."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "work-row",
          "columns": [
            {
              "type": "mykrobe-cluster",
