        {
          "type": "work-row",
          "columns": [
            {
              "text": "I rapidly developed a set of native apps with enough fidelity to enable thorough user testing with iterations of refinement and reinvention in between."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "work-row",
          "columns": [
            {
